Section [G.0] treats all the goals related to the registration to the application:-->REMOVED

Section [G.1] treats all the goals related to the creation and personalization of an event:-->REMOVED
G.1.1 The user can schedule a new event adding name, time slot, location, type of
event and a description.
G.1.2 The user can modify the name of the event.
G.1.3 The user can modify the location of the event.
G.1.4 The user can modify the description of the event.
G.1.5 The user can modify the starting time of the event.
G.1.6 The user can modify the ending time of the event.
G.1.7 The user can modify his/her event from a work event to a personal event or
viceversa.
G.1.8 The user can modify the description.
G.1.9 The user can choose how many minutes earlier arrive to his/her destination.
G.1.10 The user can delete an existing event.
G.1.11 The user can see all the events he/she has already scheduled.

Section [G.2] treats all the goals related to the customization of the Travlender preferences:-->MODIFIED
G.2.1 The user can find the quickest way to reach his events.
G.2.2 The user can find the cheapest way to reach his events.
G.2.3 The user can find the most ecological way to reach his events.
G.2.4 The user can find ways to reach to his events through means that keep him/her protected from adverse weather conditions.
G.2.5 The user can find travels for his events with selected constrains on time interval range for different transports.
G.2.6 The user can find travels for his events, with a restriction on the maximum distance with the means.
G.2.7 The user can find travels for his events with a choosen budget.
G.2.8 The user can find travels for his events with means he/she selects to use.

Section [G.3] treats all the goals related to the customization of the Travlenderâ€™s settings:-->MODIFIED
G.3.1 The user can add his/her public transports tickets or passes.-->REQUIREMENT
G.3.2 The user can select all his/her owned means.-->REQUIREMENT
G.3.3 The user can find travels through transports accessible by people with disabilities.

Section [G.4] treats all goals related to the purchase of non-shared transports:-->APPROVED
G.4.1 The user can book a taxi.
G.4.2 The user can book a limousine.

Section [G.5] treats all the goals related to the purchase of public transports:-->APPROVED
G.5.1 The user can buy a ticket for the metro.
G.5.2 The user can buy a ticket for the bus.
G.5.3 The user can buy a ticket for the trolleybus.
G.5.4 The user can buy a ticket for the tram.
G.5.5 The user can buy a ticket for the train.

Section [G.6] treats all the goals related to the purchase of shared transports:-->APPROVED
G.6.1 The user can take a bike from a bike sharing service.
G.6.2 The user can take a car from a car sharing service.

Section [G.7] treats all the goals related to the special event categories:-->REMOVED

Section [G.8] treats all the goals related to the travel:-->REMOVED


****************************************3.4.3 Security****************************************
+The system always verifies the correctness of the required data during the registration.
+The system checks the input data during the login and guarantee the access only if the credentials are verified.
